COMPLETE PROJECT STRUCTURE (All Required Files)

CORE INFRASTRUCTURE
┌─────────────────┐
│    Random       │ ← Singleton
│   Stopwatch     │ ← Singleton
│   GameEvent     │ ← Events enum
│   Observer      │ ← Pattern interfaces
│   Subject       │ ← Pattern interfaces
│   State         │ ← State pattern base
│   StateManager  │ ← State stack
│ AbstractFactory │ ← Factory pattern
└─────────────────┘
         ↓

ENTITY HIERARCHY
┌─────────────────┐
│     Entity      │ ← Abstract base
│  StaticEntity   │ ← Walls, Collectables
│ DynamicEntity   │ ← Moving entities
│   Character     │ ← PacMan & Ghosts base
│  Collectable    │ ← Coin & Fruit base
└─────────────────┘
         ↓
    ┌─────┴─────┐
    ↓           ↓
CONCRETE ENTITIES    WORLD MANAGEMENT
┌─────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────┐
│      PacMan     │  │     World       │ ← Main game orchestrator
│      Ghost      │  │    Camera       │ ← Coordinate projection
│      Coin       │  │   Collision     │ ← Detection system
│     Fruit       │  │                 │
│      Wall       │  └─────────────────┘
└─────────────────┘
         │           ↑
         └───────────┘
               ↓

SCORING & GAME FLOW
┌─────────────────┐
│      Score      │ ← Score calculation
│HighScoreManager │ ← Top 5 scores + file I/O
│   GameStates:   │
│   - MenuState   │
│   - LevelState  │
│   - PausedState │
│   - VictoryState│
│   -GameOverState│
